  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 94c46ecd48d7cdb4786744f4644a0188, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::InfoInteract
  objectTitle: Sully Pavyonu
  description: "Louvre'un do\u011Fu kanad\u0131 olan Sully Pavyonu, m\xFCzenin en
    eski b\xF6l\xFCm\xFCd\xFCr. 1546'da Pierre Lescot taraf\u0131ndan in\u015Fa edilmeye
    ba\u015Flanm\u0131\u015F, eski Louvre \u015Eatosu'nun temelleri burada bulunur.\r\n\r\nBodrum
    kat\u0131nda, 12. y\xFCzy\u0131lda II. Philippe Augustus taraf\u0131ndan yapt\u0131r\u0131lan
    orta\xE7a\u011F kalesinin kal\u0131nt\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131 gezebilirsiniz.\r\n\r\nKoleksiyonlar:\r\n-
    M\u0131s\u0131r Antikalar\u0131 (mumyalar, lahitler, hiyeroglifler)\r\n- Yak\u0131n
    Do\u011Fu Antikalar\u0131 (Hammurabi Yasas\u0131, Asur sanat\u0131)\r\n- Antik
    Yunan, Etr\xFCsk ve Roma sanat\u0131\r\n- 17.-18. y\xFCzy\u0131l Frans\u0131z
    resmi\r\n\r\nPavyonun ad\u0131 Henri IV'\xFCn ba\u015Fbakan\u0131 Maximilien
    de B\xE9thune, Duc de Sully'den gelir."
